# Solution

## O(N) Loop
Iterate over the nums vector, if
* the value is the smallest one, than update the smallest variable,
* the value is larger than current smallest value, compute the difference,
    and if the difference is the largest one, update the difference variable.

|Time|Ratio|Space|Ratio|
|----|-----|-----|-----|
|4ms|80.14%|7.9MB|99%|

